        },
        {
            "name": "Len Fellman (translation)",
            "bio": "Len Fellman is a mathematician, educator, and innovator of \"transtropilation,\" the process of translating from cantillized Hebrew, as closely as possible, “word for word and <em>trōp</em> for <em>trōp</em>”, with the main purpose being to aid a person with minimal Hebrew training in following the Hebrew leyning of the Torah and Haftarah readings word for word.",
